Get a shoutbox on you'r website with a single line of code!

The new and improvd shoutbox has some security upgrades as well as some functionality upgrades. For how to, and so on read the documentation and see the examples.

There is a thread on the matter here: http://webdevrefinery.com/forums/topic/9975-small-shoutbox-project/ , so look it up for questions and sort.

